title: Juicy J of Three 6 Mafia Joins the Show
description:
Jalen & Jacoby breakdown everything from Ja Morant’s 47-point eruption, PLUS are the Warriors in trouble with Steph and Klay going cold? AND was Dillon Brooks foul on GPII a dirty play? We discuss how the Celtics defense stepped up to Giannis in Game 2. THEN, Memphis legend, Juicy J, joins the show to talk music, Grizzlies, and pick his top 3 gentlemen’s club cities in America.
